## nginx Configuration Rules

Critical for SSE streaming — must always be present on `/api/` and `/api/sse/`:
```nginx
proxy_buffering off;
proxy_read_timeout 300s;
proxy_http_version 1.1;
proxy_set_header Connection "";
```

SPA routing — must always be present for React frontend:
```nginx
location / {
    try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
}
```

After changing nginx config:
```bash
nginx -t              # always test before reload
nginx -s reload       # graceful reload, no downtime
```

